  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa2">
<l>vaiyattu vāḻvīrkāḷ nāmum nampāvaikkuc</l>
<l>ceyyum kiricaikaḷ kēḷīrō pāṟkaṭaluḷ</l>
<l>paiyat tuyiṉṟa paramaṉaṭi pāṭi</l>
<l>neyyuṇṇōm pāluṇṇōm nāṭkālē nīrāṭi</l>
<l>maiyiṭṭu eḻutōm malariṭṭu nām muṭiyōm</l>
<l>ceyyātaṉa ceyyōm tīkkuṟaḷaic ceṉṟōtōm</l>
<l>aiyamum piccaiyum āntaṉaiyum kai kāṭṭi</l>
<l>uyyumāṟ eṇṇi ukantēlōr empāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O those who live on [this] earth!</l>
<l>Won’t you listen [about] the rites that we are going to perform for our Pāvai[-vow]?</l>
<l>Singing about the feet of the Supreme Being who gently slept on the milk ocean,</l>
<l rend="indent">We shall not eat ghee,</l>
<l rend="indent">we shall not drink milk.</l>
<l>Bathing in the early morning,</l>
<l rend="indent">We shall not paint [our eyes] using kohl.</l>
<l rend="indent">We shall not adorn [our hair] placing flowers.</l>
<l rend="indent">We shall not do that which is not [to be] done.</l>
<l rend="indent">	We shall not go and speak evil calumny.</l>
<l>Giving a little alms [and] food charity as much as possible,</l>
<l>Pondering on the path to redemption</l>
<l>[we shall] rejoice,</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
